{"tid":810806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓水災 至少76人喪生","createTime":"2018-09-08T09:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T11:18:49.000Z","uid":179810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c386d98dc6c500bd0662f79381c33f8b9e0b106","tid":810806,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:24:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>國際救援組織稱北韓近日嚴重水浸　至少76人死亡</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n2018-09-07 HKT 11:13<br />\r\n<br />\r\n總部設在瑞士日內瓦的紅十字會與紅新月會國際聯合會表示，北韓近日出現嚴重水災，造成至少76人死亡、75人失蹤，失蹤者有很多是兒童，數千人無家可歸，組織展開搜索及救援行動。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n組織表示，北韓黃海南道及及黃海北道，自8月底以來連日降雨，低窪地區出現大規模水浸及土石流，造成800多戶民宅、診所及學校等建築損毀，數千人無家可歸，急需醫療設備、食物、潔淨食水及衛生設備。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n北韓紅十字會表示，已持續向災民提供援助，並會提供淨水設備。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n組織早前警告，<span style=\"color: red;\">熱浪侵襲導致北韓稻米和玉米等農作物枯萎</span>，當地可能爆發嚴重的糧食危機。<br />\r\n<br />\r\nlink:<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1416621-20180907.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1416621-20180907.htm&d=uQwPir3gsIxEKPjvnYVJgaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=d6741a77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1416621-20180907.htm&h=bd195cb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1416621-20180907.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n北泡人命貴高中國"},{"pid":"916bcfc687d0dadeb1fa9bcf6e44450762c81620","tid":810806,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"熱浪咁危險下次都係食pizza味算"},{"pid":"ce5a55bb58883cb9edeafa1b8c1154d6f83c76b2","tid":810806,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:46:12.000Z","msg":"做北泡人真係重刷好過"},{"pid":"a92aba35617a9bd8f7cfabbd987af7ceae7b6fb5","tid":810806,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"916bcfc687d0dadeb1fa9bcf6e44450762c81620","tid":810806,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"熱浪咁危險下次都係食pizza味算"},"citedBy"